  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Sharp\" title=\"House Sharp\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/50px-None.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/75px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/100px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Harmund Sharp</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Sharp\" title=\"House Sharp\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/50px-None.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/75px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/100px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Sharp\" title=\"House Sharp\">House Sharp</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Harrag_Sharp\" title=\"Harrag Sharp\">Harrag Sharp</a></li><li>Sons<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Harmund Sharp</b> is a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Sharp\" title=\"House Sharp\">House Sharp</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harmund_Sharp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Harmund has many sons, including <a href=\"/index.php/Harrag_Sharp\" title=\"Harrag Sharp\">Harrag Sharp</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harmund_Sharp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harmund_Sharp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Harmund is a supporter of <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> During the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot\" title=\"Kingsmoot\">kingsmoot</a>, Asha explains that his son <a href=\"/index.php/Harrag_Sharp\" title=\"Harrag Sharp\">Harrag</a> died at <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Sack of Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> for turnips.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harmund_Sharp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Asha</b>: Harmund Sharp, your son <a href=\"/index.php/Harrag_Sharp\" title=\"Harrag Sharp\">Harrag</a> died at <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Sack of Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, for this. You have other sons, I think. If you'd trade their lives for turnips, shout <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">my nuncle's</a> name!<br /><b>Harmund</b>: And if I shout your name? What then?<br /><b>Asha</b>: Peace. Land. Victory.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a> and Harmund</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harmund_Sharp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_19\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 19\">Chapter 19</a>, The Drowned Man.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403134242\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.093 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.305 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 749/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10636/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6943/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 760/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1815/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.200/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.43 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  292.909      1 -total\n 96.46%  282.547      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.79%  280.572      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.59%   33.942     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.97%   11.639      5 Template:Ref\n  3.11%    9.107      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.38%    6.968      5 Template:Ref/core\n  0.78%    2.289      1 Template:Quote\n  0.66%    1.931      1 Template:References\n  0.34%    1.001      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:5488-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403134242 and revision id 295839\n -->\n",
